org.anchoranalysis.io.manifest.directory

Class MutableDirectory

  • Object
    • MutableDirectory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, SequencedDirectory, WriteOperationRecorder
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RootDirectory, SubdirectoryBase

    public abstract class MutableDirectory
extends Object
implements SequencedDirectory, WriteOperationRecorder, Serializable
    An entry for a directory in the manifest, to which outputs and sub-directories can be later added.

    By implementing the WriteOperationRecorder interface, it accepts write operations for files and subdirectories, which are handled differently by the various sub-classes of MutableDirectory.

    Author:
    Owen Feehan
